CORTEZ OIL COMPANY v. Acel C. ALEXANDER, Collector. No. 525. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Jan. 11, 1932. Hunter L. Johnson, of Tulsa, Okl., for appellant. - Herbert K. Hyde, U. S. Atty., of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellee.

Before LEWIS and COTTERAL, Circuit Judges, and KENNAMER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on application of appellant.
